  "Description": {
    "English": "Equip this exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Personal Flair</span> in commemoration of the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Utopia</span> expedition, and contributions to the Utopia Foundation communal habitation project.<br><br>Apply this banner to your profile at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
